    <div class="content-item document">    <h2 class="header"><span>ABOUT US</span></h2>
<div class="document-container">
    <p>Welcome to Packaging Network, the preeminent Internet source for useful and timely information about the packaging industry. If you are involved in the engineering, production, purchasing, design, or marketing of packaging equipment or materials, you now have instant, free access to a comprehensive web site that delivers the latest information on the industry.</p>

<p>The Packaging Network database serves the information needs of engineers, corporate managers, business executives, general managers, and others involved in the production, purchase, design, or marketing of packaging for all consumer and industrial products.</p>

<p>Reflecting the dynamic and interactive character of the Internet, Packaging Network is the most convenient source of technical, operational, product, management, and regulatory/legal information available for the packaging industry.</p>

<p>Please take a moment to <a href="http://www.packagingnetwork.com/user/New">join our community</a> and discover the benefits of your free membership.</p>

<p>Who are our clients? The leading manufacturers in the packaging industry have recognized the benefits of being part of an online community for this vertical market. Packaging Network offers a way for their customers and prospects to cut through the clutter of the Internet and put their company in a position to be discovered in an increasingly crowded medium. <a href="mailto:info@packagingnetwork.com">Contact us</a> today for advertising information.</p>

<p>How it all began. . .Packaging Network was first launched by VertMarkets, Inc. in June 1998 with two lofty goals: First, to become the leading source of product technology, standards, management and news information in the packaging industry, and second, to create and foster an atmosphere in which engineers, managers, producers, purchasers, designers, and marketers in this industry can keep easily abreast of developments, as well as identify and communicate with those advertisers in Packaging Network who can satisfy their business needs.</p>

<p>If you have any comments or questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@packagingnetwork.com">info@packagingnetwork.com</a>.</p>

</div></div>
 
